0:{"buildId":"I3GEKSVLVTWqxcEXDRaWq","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"ISO Certification Audit"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:31:19+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"ISO Auditors are key to the success of the ISO Certification in UAE. The ISO Auditors will assess the organizations current stage and devise the corrective"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO Certification Audit"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO Certification Audit is done by ISO Auditors in UAE. ISO Auditors are key to the success of the ISO Certification in UAE. The ISO Auditors will assess the organizations current stage and devise the corrective measures to fully optimize the ISO Quality Management System of the organization."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The auditors must audit the policy manuals to ensure that right documentation is in place for meeting the requirements of ISO Certification in UAE. The document must include policies and procedures to increase the performance of the organization and the employees must follow the ISO Standard and comply with it."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Certification Auditor:"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The ISO Certification auditor will usually audits only one ISO standard at a time. However, the auditor is experienced in a diverse of ISO Standards."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Take the assistance of the auditor to get ISO certified for the right ISO Standard for your organization. The organization must provide all the required information and help the auditor to complete the audit effectively."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How ISO Auditor in UAE will Assist you to get ISO Certification?"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO Auditor in UAE will ask for assistance on the scope of ISO certification and the auditor request for required documents and perform inspection around the premises. The senior management must make sure that the documentation and required information are readily available. Inform the employee to be supportive to the inspection and audit to build a positive rapport among the ISO Auditor in UAE. The Auditor will again visit the organization during the surveillance audit."}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The ISO Certification auditor is not eligible to provide any ISO consulting. Hence the absence of non-conformity will force the auditor to mark non-compliance with the Certification and provide a report for re-audit."}]]}],["$","footer",null,{"className":"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":["$L2","$L3","$L4","$L5","$L6","$L7","$L8","$L9","$La"]}]}]]}]}],["$Lb"],"$Lc"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
